high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn left to the round table, go to the table.
Take the watch to the right of the box from the table.
Turn around, go forward a step, turn left, go forward to the coffee table, turn left, go forward to the left side of the couch, turn left, go forward to the round table.
Put the watch on the silver plate on the table.
Take the plate from the table.
Turn left, go forward, turn left to face the coffee table, go to the coffee table.
Put the plate behind the statue on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a watch on it on a coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and then turn left towards the table.
Pick the watch up from the table.
Turn around, go left towards the small table, turn left, go towards the couch and then turn left towards the big table.
Put the watch on the gray tray on the table.
Pick up the tray from the table.
Turn around and head to the small table.
Put the tray on the small table behind the statue.
anns.task_desc: Put a tray with a watch on it on the small table.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the round table in the corner.
Pick up the watch between the cardboard box and the newspaper, on the table.
Step back from the table and turn to your right, walk just past the table and turn left, then go to the arm of the couch and turn to your left again.
Place the watch on the square plate, on the table.
Pick up the plate with the watch on it.
Turn around and go to the coffee table in front of you.
Place the plate with the watch on it on the table, closest to the couch, in front of the statue.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate containing a watch on the coffee table.
